name: TezCasino - Tezos Lotto (30tez winner!)
description:
Welcome to the first collection from the TezCasino! 
This collection is a lottery featuring 30 tickets with one winner!
Each ticket costs 1tez and the winner of the lottery will receive 30tez!

How to enter the lottery:
1.) Buy a lottery ticket here for 1tez!
2.) Wait for all other tickets to be bought!
3.) Winner will be announced on Twitter: @Kakashi_tez

Feel free to DM @Kakashi_tez on Twitter with any questions or concerns and we plan to make a discord for TezCasino after this collection.

Good luck to all participants and enjoy yourself at the TezCasino!
